{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji46","name":"毛泽东全集第46卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji46.pdf"],"article":{"title":"关于胡芷芸案件的指示","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"关于胡芷芸案件的指示!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1964年4月）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看，确有此事吧！有些人只爱物，不爱人，只重生产，不重改造。把犯人当成劳役，只有压服不行。其实，抓紧思想政治工作，以思想工作第一，做好这一面，不仅不会妨碍生产，相反还会促进生产。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是1964年4月，毛泽东和公安部副部长汪东兴谈话的一部分。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":4}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":355,"page_end":355},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"指示"}]}]}